parameters:
\N<National Language Teacher> Um... I have a sudden
announcement.

taking over as the homeroom teacher for this class from Mr.
Omura.

various circumstances, and he can no longer continue as a
teacher.

\N<National Language Teacher> Could you please be quiet?
\N<National Language Teacher> And one more thing...

\N<National Language Teacher> One of our classmates, <K
Hinata Aki>, will be leaving school.

\N<National Language Teacher> It's due to family
circumstances.

\N<Female student> I... I heard a rumor, but it seems that
she's actually... <Kpregnant>...‼
\N<Students>\{ Ehhhh!?

huh!

like with Omura and Aki's families?
\N<Male students> Wow, it's definitely true, right!
\N<National Language Teacher> You all, be quiet.
